    <h2>Practical exercise - <span class="keyword">Setting up a game repo</span></h2>

    <div class="quest-objective">
      <p>Configure a Git repository with LFS for a fictional video game project. You'll create the structure, configure LFS, and simulate a workflow with binary files.</p>
