    <h3>Step 1 - Create the repository and initialize LFS</h3>

    <pre data-lang="bash"><code># Create the project
mkdir titans-forges-project
cd titans-forges-project
git init

# Initialize LFS
git lfs install</code></pre>

    <pre data-lang="powershell"><code># Create the project
mkdir titans-forges-project
cd titans-forges-project
git init

# Initialize LFS
git lfs install</code></pre>

    <h3>Step 2 - Configure files to track</h3>

    <pre data-lang="bash"><code># Track common binary file types
git lfs track "*.png"
git lfs track "*.jpg"
git lfs track "*.psd"
git lfs track "*.wav"
git lfs track "*.mp3"
git lfs track "*.fbx"
git lfs track "*.blend"

# Verify that .gitattributes was created
cat .gitattributes</code></pre>

    <pre data-lang="powershell"><code># Track common binary file types
